      "description" : "Overnight, you cycled through Linkin Park’s “One More Light” and Derek & The Dominos’ “Layla” with clockwork regularity, weaving in country detours and grunge anthems. By afternoon, Stone Temple Pilots and Nirvana circled back for encore spins. 336 minutes, 105 tracks, 24 repeats—your most replayed day of the year.",
